59
00:02:36,740 --> 00:02:39,245
the continental or
planetary scale.

60
00:02:39,245 --> 00:02:43,540
In 2015, in a science
advances paper,

61
00:02:43,540 --> 00:02:45,860
scientists characterize
the state of

62
00:02:45,860 --> 00:02:48,905
seven out of the nine
planetary boundaries.

63
00:02:48,905 --> 00:02:51,830
We'll start by focusing
on climate change,

64
00:02:51,830 --> 00:02:53,515
which is right here at the top.

65
00:02:53,515 --> 00:02:54,730
We can already see,

66
00:02:54,730 --> 00:02:56,390
it's already out of

67
00:02:56,390 --> 00:02:58,910
