bring us back down.

123
00:05:21,890 --> 00:05:26,525
What are the causes
of climate change?

124
00:05:26,525 --> 00:05:28,280
Well, like I said,

125
00:05:28,280 --> 00:05:30,080
we believe it's
greenhouse gases,

126
00:05:30,080 --> 00:05:31,610
and the reason that
scientists have

127
00:05:31,610 --> 00:05:33,485
confidence in that is because

128
00:05:33,485 --> 00:05:35,060
the observed warming matches

129
00:05:35,060 --> 00:05:37,260
