202
00:08:31,290 --> 00:08:35,715
4,000, or 3,000
gigatons of CO_2.

203
00:08:35,715 --> 00:08:38,105
Then on the vertical
axis of Panel B,

204
00:08:38,105 --> 00:08:39,830
we can see what that
would mean in terms of

205
00:08:39,830 --> 00:08:41,830
